'''鴿乳'''，又稱'''嗉囊乳'''，是親代鳥類從[[嗉囊|嗉囊]]中[[反芻|反芻]]給雛鳥的一種分泌物。所有[[鸠鸽科|鸠鸽科]]鳥類都能夠分泌這種物質，此外有此能力的還有[[火烈鳥|火烈鳥]]和一些[[企鵝|企鵝]]。<ref name="Levi">{{cite book |last=Levi |first=Wendell |title= The Pigeon|year= 1977|publisher= Levi Publishing Co, Inc|location= Sumter, S.C.|isbn=0-85390-013-2 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Silver|first=Rae|title=Prolactin and Parenting in the Pigeon Family|journal=The Journal of Experimental Zoology|volume=232|pages=617–625|year=1984|url=http://www.columbiauniversity.org/cu/psychology/silver/publications/035Silver%201984.PDF|doi=10.1002/jez.1402320330|pmid=6394702|issue=3|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160913135843/http://www.columbiauniversity.org/cu/psychology/silver/publications/035Silver%201984.PDF|archivedate=2016-09-13|access-date=2013-09-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal| author=Eraud, C., Dorie, A., Jacquet, A. and Faivre, B. |year=2008| title= The crop milk: a potential new route for carotenoid-mediated parental effects| journal=Journal of Avian Biology| volume=39| pages=247–251| doi=10.1111/j.0908-8857.2008.04053.x| issue=2}}</ref>

== 與哺乳動物乳的區別 ==

鴿乳與[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]的[[乳|乳]]沒有太大的相似之處。前者只是一種淺黃色的半固體狀物質，而後者屬於[[乳劑|乳劑]]的範疇，<ref name= Gillespie2011>{{cite journal|date=2011-09-19|title=Histological and global gene expression analysis of the 'lactating' pigeon crop|pages=452|volume=12|issn=1471-2164|url=https://doi.org/10.1186/1471-2164-12-452|doi=10.1186/1471-2164-12-452|journal=BMC Genomics|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Meagan J. Gillespie, Volker R. Haring, Kenneth A. McColl, Paul Monaghan, John A. Donald, Kevin R. Nicholas, Robert J. Moore, Tamsyn M. Crowley}}</ref> 鴿乳比[[牛乳|牛乳]]和[[人乳|人乳]]更富含[[蛋白質|蛋白質]]和[[脂肪|脂肪]]。<ref>Ehrlich, Paul R.; Dobkin, David S. and Wheye, Darryl (1988)  [http://www.stanford.edu/group/stanfordbirds/text/essays/Bird_Milk.html Bird Milk] {{Wayback|url=http://www.stanford.edu/group/stanfordbirds/text/essays/Bird_Milk.html |date=20121015052523 }}. stanford.edu</ref> 它還含有抗氧化劑和免疫增強因子。<ref>[http://www.australiangeographic.com.au/journal/birds-produce-milk-similar-to-mammals.htm "Mysteries of pigeon milk explained"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.australiangeographic.com.au/journal/birds-produce-milk-similar-to-mammals.htm |date=20110924022121 }} Retrieved September 22, 2011</ref> 如哺乳動物的乳汁一樣，鴿乳含[[免疫球蛋白A|IgA]]抗體，亦有一些種類的細菌。<ref name=Gillespie2012>{{cite journal|title=Functional Similarities between Pigeon ‘Milk’ and Mammalian Milk: Induction of Immune Gene Expression and Modification of the Microbiota|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0048363|url=http://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0048363|date=2012-10-26|journal=PLOS ONE|volume=7|issue=10|pages=e48363|issn=1932-6203|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Meagan J. Gillespie, Dragana Stanley, Honglei Chen, John A. Donald, Kevin R. Nicholas, Robert J. Moore, Tamsyn M. Crowley|archive-date=2018-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615101132/http://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0048363|dead-url=no}}</ref> 火烈鳥和鴿類無論雌雄都可以分泌鴿乳哺育後代，而企鵝中只有雄性才有此能力。<ref name=Gillespie2012/> 在哺乳期同哺乳類一樣由[[催乳激素|催乳激素]]刺激分泌。<ref name=Gillespie2012/>

